# Media, rights, and privacy

## Media
- Store images in object storage, not as base64 in DB.
- Do not hotlink external images as final card images.
- Save provider/source/license/provenance metadata.
- Admin must be able to review media rights status.

## Privacy
- Support privacy settings.
- Support data export request and deletion/anonymization flow skeleton.
- Protect user-level analytics drill-down with RBAC and audit reason.
- Avoid exposing personal information in public leaderboard/battle views by default.
